{"tid":14063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[急問] 澳洲被入屋爆竊","createTime":"2016-11-30T10:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T11:25:57.000Z","uid":38915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7241cb811865f9413afa9934d133e508192afb9f","tid":14063,"uid":38915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:47:50.000Z","msg":"老死係澳洲讀書住SHARE HOUSE<br />\n比人爆窗入屋<br />\n<br />\n損失點算大約係咁：<br />\n自己：HDD + ATM卡<br />\n室友：成部腦<br />\n<br />\n先撇除幾十年珍藏一瞬間無晒<br />\n入面好多重要既、學校功課PJ、<br />\n證書副本、相之類。<br />\n<br />\n只得個睇落無咩用既機箱barcode<br />\n同埋部份零件既單，上面有寫到HDD既Serial No.<br />\n<br />\n雖然我估都估到賊會分件賣或者自用<br />\n但都幫佢問下循例問下<br />\n差佬話食個飯聽朝先散步過黎<br />\n<br />\n無人可以教下應該點做好。<br />\n好迷惘。"},{"pid":"134474123454b70f3eebadcd8ce4a0555b0c10bc","tid":14063,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"225ca527db1a33e6bcfdb520e6b646789c49be78","tid":14063,"uid":46281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d56c22d0e939b06a9b2ad60f819d193f6ef6b9a","tid":14063,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"除左報警重可以點？"},{"pid":"6a3f250a08e7560baff779e406bfab6319f835bd","tid":14063,"uid":36632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"冇野可以做 澳洲警察做野hea到仆街"},{"pid":"244ad6265956b135cbad16676cafd011bf403c57","tid":14063,"uid":4144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:56:44.000Z","msg":"上次揸車比人撞 打佐電話報警 等佐個半鍾無人黎 之後自己去醫院"},{"pid":"46afb3c8007b7dbd3859829389c1f4387f531baf","tid":14063,"uid":28024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"報警<br />\n拎警察file number<br />\n同學校傾assignment 要延期<br />\n<br />\nBy the way 有冇家居保險？"},{"pid":"14b9146d2e5021d78475c1f7d4e11dedc8a1cc2e","tid":14063,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0